Usage: ON [#|+|-|^|&|@]NOTIFY_SIGNON_UH [-|^]<parameters> [action]
  This is activated when someone on your notify list (see
  NOTIFY) signs onto irc and the username and the
  hostname of person who signed on are known.
  The parameters to the action are:
    $0  Nickname of person who signed on
    $1  Username of person who signed on
    $2  Hostname of person who signed on
